  1. Find all full medicine programs (Tp but not Tp Mhendislii) of foundation universities group by university calculate total quotas per university and maximum max_score and minimum min_score as bounds, ordered and colored by total quota. (Tip: Use geom_crossbar)

We can again use grepl to find requested programs:

medicals <- osym_data_2017 %>% filter(grepl("Tp", program_name)) %>% 
    filter(!grepl("Mhendis", program_name))
medicals <- medicals %>% group_by(university_name) %>% summarise(total_quota = sum(as.numeric(general_quota)), 
    max = max(max_score), min = min(min_score))
print(medicals)
